{"tid":2253003,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"教宗方濟各首表態支持同性民事結合：同為上主兒女，應立法讓他們受保障","createTime":"2020-10-22T01:07:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-22T01:15:15.000Z","uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2f656e32a59e8b884755388f757f4a9403abe9cc","tid":2253003,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T01:07:51.000Z","msg":"教宗方濟各在一齣紀錄片中表明支持同性民事結合 (Civil Union) ，是首位支持民事結合的教宗，一改梵蒂岡過往對同性關係立場。<br />\n<br />\n周三於羅馬電影節首映的紀錄片訪問了教宗方濟各，訪談討論了環境、貧窮、移民、種族、收入不公，以及受歧視的小眾。方濟各指：「同性戀者有權成為家庭的一份子，他們同為上主的兒女，有權擁有自己的家庭。誰都不應因此而被趕走或被害慘。我們應訂立民事結合法律。這樣將讓他們受法律保障。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E6%95%99%E5%AE%97%E6%96%B9%E6%BF%9F%E5%90%84%E9%A6%96%E8%A1%A8%E6%85%8B%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E5%90%8C%E6%80%A7%E6%B0%91%E4%BA%8B%E7%B5%90%E5%90%88-%E5%90%8C%E7%82%BA%E4%B8%8A%E4%B8%BB%E5%85%92%E5%A5%B3-%E6%87%89%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E8%AE%93%E4%BB%96%E5%80%91%E5%8F%97%E4%BF%9D%E9%9A%9C/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%25AE%2597%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%25BF%259F%25E5%2590%2584%25E9%25A6%2596%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E6%2585%258B%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258C%2581%25E5%2590%258C%25E6%2580%25A7%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25BA%258B%25E7%25B5%2590%25E5%2590%2588-%25E5%2590%258C%25E7%2582%25BA%25E4%25B8%258A%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%2585%2592%25E5%25A5%25B3-%25E6%2587%2589%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E8%25AE%2593%25E4%25BB%2596%25E5%2580%2591%25E5%258F%2597%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%259A%259C%2F&d=mhl3ai6H9Odyk596tiaOPd8yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=dc3e6373\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%25AE%2597%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%25BF%259F%25E5%2590%2584%25E9%25A6%2596%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E6%2585%258B%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258C%2581%25E5%2590%258C%25E6%2580%25A7%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25BA%258B%25E7%25B5%2590%25E5%2590%2588-%25E5%2590%258C%25E7%2582%25BA%25E4%25B8%258A%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%2585%2